## (b) Exact cfg lines if you wire ILM anyway

Follow install `live.cfg` priorities **1–6**, below snow (7) / swgsource (8) / searchPath (9–10). **Omit `ILM_ui.tre`.**

```cfg
	searchTree_00_1="D:/Code/SWGSource Client v3.0/ILM_sound.tre"
	searchTree_00_2="D:/Code/SWGSource Client v3.0/ILM_maps.tre"
	searchTree_00_3="D:/Code/SWGSource Client v3.0/ILM_music.tre"
	searchTree_00_4="D:/Code/SWGSource Client v3.0/ILM_visuals.tre"
	searchTree_00_5="D:/Code/SWGSource Client v3.0/ILM_animation.tre"
```

Also ensure this stays (required, not optional):

```cfg
	searchPath_00_9="D:/Code/SWGSource Client v3.0/"
```

Add to `tools/setup/client.cfg.template` so regen doesn’t drop it.

